flowchart TB
    subgraph Intake [Submission Intake]
        BrokerPortal[Broker Portal /<br/>Email Inbox]
        AcordParser[Acord XML Parser /<br/>LLM Document Extraction]
    end

    subgraph Core [Core Insurance Platform]
        PAS[Policy Administration System<br/>Guidewire / Duck Creek / Majesco]
        Billing[Billing System]
        ClaimsSys[Claims System]
    end

    subgraph UWLayer [Underwriting Layer]
        Workbench[Underwriter Workbench<br/>Unified submission view]
        Rating[Rating Engine<br/>Earnix / Akur8 / Guidewire]
        RulesEng[Underwriting Rules Engine]
        Triage[ML Triage Scoring]
    end

    subgraph DataLayer [Data Enrichment]
        LN[LexisNexis<br/>C.L.U.E. / MVR / Attract]
        MIB[MIB / Rx<br/>Life underwriting]
        Verisk[Verisk / ISO<br/>Loss costs, RMS cat]
        Imagery[Cape Analytics /<br/>Betterview / EagleView]
        Hazard[HazardHub /<br/>First Street]
        DB[D&B / Experian<br/>Business data]
        Sanctions[OFAC / PEP<br/>Sanctions screening]
    end

    subgraph ReInsurance [Reinsurance]
        CessionMgmt[Cession Management<br/>Sapiens / Guidewire]
        TreatySys[Treaty Admin]
    end

    subgraph ML [ML Platform]
        ModelServing[Model Serving<br/>SageMaker / Databricks]
        FeatureStore[Feature Store]
        Governance[Model Governance<br/>& Explainability]
    end

    subgraph Downstream [Reporting]
        DataLake[Data Lake<br/>Underwriting data warehouse]
        BI[BI / Dashboards]
        RegRep[Regulatory Reporting<br/>Solvency II / RBC / IFRS17]
    end

    BrokerPortal --> AcordParser
    AcordParser --> Workbench
    Workbench --> PAS
    Workbench <--> Rating
    Workbench <--> RulesEng
    Workbench --> Triage

    Workbench -.calls.-> LN
    Workbench -.calls.-> MIB
    Workbench -.calls.-> Verisk
    Workbench -.calls.-> Imagery
    Workbench -.calls.-> Hazard
    Workbench -.calls.-> DB
    Workbench -.calls.-> Sanctions

    Triage --> ModelServing
    Rating -.may call.-> ModelServing
    ModelServing <--> FeatureStore
    ModelServing --> Governance

    PAS --> Billing
    PAS --> ClaimsSys
    PAS --> CessionMgmt
    CessionMgmt --> TreatySys

    PAS --> DataLake
    ClaimsSys --> DataLake
    CessionMgmt --> DataLake
    DataLake --> BI
    DataLake --> RegRep

